## Global options

| Option | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `--verbose` | Enable verbose output |
| `--json` | Output in JSON format |
| `--version` | Print version information |
| `--help` | Print help |

## Commands

### `info`

Display version, build, and environment information.

```bash
{{ project_name }} info
{{ project_name }} info --json
```

### `completions`

Generate shell completions.

```bash
{{ project_name }} completions bash
{{ project_name }} completions zsh
{{ project_name }} completions fish
{{ project_name }} completions powershell
```
{% if has_config %}

### `doctor`

Check configuration and environment health.

```bash
{{ project_name }} doctor
```
{%- endif %}
